com.reactivecascade.i

Interface IRunnableAltFuture<IN,OUT>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAltFuture<IN,OUT>, IAsyncOrigin, ICancellable, IGettable<OUT>, ISafeGettable<OUT>, Runnable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RunnableAltFuture

    public interface IRunnableAltFuture<IN,OUT>
extends IAltFuture<IN,OUT>, Runnable
    A future value which will execute an IAction before the value is determined. The output of the action may determine the value, or the IAltFuture.getUpchain() value is used if no value is output by the action.

    See also ISettableAltFuture
